too high. Therefore, a complete cycle consists of these three overlapping layers. When these three layers resonate, it presents a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity. The 2008 financial crisis exemplifies this. At the time, there was extreme panic, with volatility indices soaring above 80. Central banks around the world began to inject liquidity, and the

