Reserve drastically reduced interest rates to zero, initiating quantitative easing. The eve of the mobile internet technology revolution saw the release of the iPhone, the establishment of the App Store, and the initial widespread adoption of 3G networks. When these three cycles resonate simultaneously, a bull market lasting over a decade ensues. The Nasdaq

