00:20:30,500 --> 00:20:33,200
after 2009, and this is happening in China today. Regarding the technology industry, many believe it experiences exponential growth without cycles. We can only say that innovation is endless, but specific technology sectors always have cycles. The dot-com bubble of 2000 saw the

